This is a catch-all noticeboard for the [[VRCWiki:Team|VRCWiki Team]]. It is also a place where the VRCWiki Team may make some announcements for transparency regarding recent Maintainer actions.

Some things that can be posted here:

* Incidents on the wiki needing VRCWiki staff to intervene, such as violations of policies
* Requests for page protection
* Deletion requests
* Block requests

For '''Urgent incidents''', consider also contacting a Maintainer via [[Discord servers#VRChat_Wiki|The VRCWiki Discord]].

Any user of the wiki can comment on discussion, as long as that comment is constructive and civil. In general, Maintainers will close these discussions.

'''[[Special:NewSection/VRCWiki:Maintainers Noticeboard|To add a new section to this noticeboard, click here.]]''' Make sure to sign your post with 4 tildes (<nowiki>~~~~</nowiki>) before hitting "post".

